I am very disappointed in my newly bought Samsung phone model A17 5G the battery drains fast even when lighter used just messenger,very poor camera if your ugly you will be uglier,poor in call volume you can't clearly hear when someone is in call. I went to the store to replace it because it's still under the warranty of 7 Day's replacement,the store advice me to go to the service center for checking before they will accept it. So I went to the service center but then it dissapoint me even more.

I stopped doing updates as there are always unfixable problems and things I liked taken away why samsung doesn't have an IT team that can get it right without problems is beyond me very unprofessional. I've had several models and my latest is S24 but each update always comes with problems. I've asked if there are problems with the next update and got the answer YES AND WE'RE WORKING ON IT. NOT GOOD ENOUGH SAMSUNG.
